      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, drain your<strong> king</strong> <strong>prawns</strong>, then add them to a bowl with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Add<strong> half</strong> your <strong>shichimi togarashi </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and give everything a good stir until the prawns are completely coated – these are your <strong>togarashi prawns</strong></p><p>Set aside to marinate</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1690355605575-x200.jpg",
