            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>sriracha</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) with your <strong>mayo</strong> and a splash of <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl – this is your<strong> sriracha mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
