        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong> in half lengthways, around the stone</p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely lengthways</p><p>Drizzle your <strong>rice vinegar </strong>over the <strong>sliced avocado</strong></p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p>",
