    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sushi rice is cooked, remove the dish from the oven, pour your <strong>mirin</strong> over the rice, then top the rice with the <strong>togarashi prawns</strong></p><p>Return the dish to the oven for a further 6-7 min or until the prawns are cooked through – this is your<strong> king prawn 'sushi' rice bake</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
