    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>king</strong> <strong>prawn 'sushi' rice bake </strong>topped with the<strong> sliced avocado</strong> and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>tamari</strong> <strong>soy sauce </strong>and <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>shichimi togarashi </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and your <strong>seaweed flakes</strong></p><p>Dig in!</p>",
